params.name: input_ids
params.description: The watermark generated text. It is advised to remove the prompt, which can affect the detection.

params.name: z_threshold
params.description: Changing this threshold will change the sensitivity of the detector. Higher z threshold gives lesssensitivity and vice versa for lower z threshold.

params.name: return_dict
params.description: Whether to return ~generation.WatermarkDetectorOutput or not. If not it will return boolean predictions,
